Before running this folder, the **ruleName** needs to be set in the **Pre-request script.** The **ruleName** indicates the rule that all rule components in the datafile will go under. You can quickly get the names of all the rules from another tag property:

```
{{HOST}}properties/:propID/rules

```

Once the **ruleName** has been set, this folder should be run as a collection runner with a datafile. The datafile should be an array of rule components exported from another tag property:

``` plaintext
GET {{HOST}}/rules/:currentRule/rule_components

```

